contentrichtext.text: {{Expand French|date=December 2008|Barbeville}} {{Infobox French commune |name = Barbeville |region = Basse-Normandie |department = Calvados |arrondissement = Bayeux |canton = Bayeux |INSEE = 14040 |postal code = 14400 |mayor = Denis Énée |term = 2008–2014 |intercommunality = Bayeux Intercom |longitude = -0.7478 |latitude = 49.2756 |elevation m = 53 |elevation min m = 22 |elevation max m = 62 |area km2 = 3.47 |population = 182 |population date = 2008 }} '''Barbeville''' is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Calvados]] [[Departments of France|department]] in the [[Basse-Normandie]] [[Regions of France|region]] in northwestern [[France]]. ==Population== {{Historical populations |align=left |1962|169 |1968|196 |1975|181 |1982|174 |1990|151 |1999|163 |2008|182 }} {{clear-left}} ==See also== *[[Communes of the Calvados department]] ==References== *[http://www.insee.fr/en/home/home_page.asp INSEE] {{reflist}} {{Calvados communes}} [[Category:Communes of Calvados]] {{Calvados-geo-stub}}
